---
title: Louisiana Pork & Creamy Slaw with Sesame Carrot Fries & Aioli Dressing
description: Give pork loin a dash of flair with a smokey Louisiana spice blend for a melody of robust flavours. Then, don’t stop there. Ramp
up your dish with a creamy Dijon aioli slaw tossed around with cucumber. With the added bonus of this tasty delight being low carb, this one’s an exciting ride from start to finish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
